55:26.120 --> 55:27.756
it can be awkward
when I bump into friends

55:27.789 --> 55:28.690
on the bus.'"

55:30.892 --> 55:33.662
"Katja found a job
as an in-house typographer

55:33.696 --> 55:36.098
in an agency in Dublin.

55:36.131 --> 55:38.267
