at the departure lounge

55:38.300 --> 55:40.702
clutching an overpriced
caramel latte.

55:40.736 --> 55:43.306
I said, 'Don't be a stranger.'

55:44.372 --> 55:48.943
She kissed my hand, winked,
and disappeared through customs.

55:48.977 --> 55:51.714
I went home,
watched <i>Dirty Dancing,</i>

55:51.747 --> 55:53.683
and ate cereal from a mug."

55:55.117 --> 55:56.419
<i>Efcharistó.</i>

56:00.122 --> 56:01.190
Thank you, Jovana.

56:01.222 --> 56:03.258
That was very enjoyable.

56:04.193 --> 56:07.430
I have many comments,
but I will open it to the floor.

56:07.463 --> 56:09.932
- Anyone have a question, yes?
- Yes.

56:09.964 --> 56:11.434
Hello, Jovana.

56:11.466 --> 56:13.968
