57:11.827 --> 57:12.962
I don't...

57:12.995 --> 57:13.763
I don't speak Greek,

57:13.796 --> 57:15.097
but I kind
of get your point, yeah?

57:17.265 --> 57:19.068
Um, Jovana, I'm just saying,

57:19.100 --> 57:20.769
