for Calvin Klein

57:20.803 --> 57:22.338
like Tiny Banderas over here,

57:22.370 --> 57:23.772
but I'm going
to front my videos,

57:23.805 --> 57:25.173
not hide behind a facade.

57:36.285 --> 57:37.787
My apologies, everybody.

57:38.921 --> 57:40.990
Yes, yes up the back there?

57:41.022 --> 57:48.430
<i>♪ Silence is your enemy ♪</i>

57:48.463 --> 57:50.265
<i>You could
cut the tension with a knife.</i>

57:50.298 --> 57:52.434
<i>So the question remains,</i>

57:52.466 --> 57:55.271
<i>did Jovana Fey
sleep with a hundred women?</i>

57:55.303 --> 57:56.939
Ooh!

57:56.972 --> 58:00.376
Okay, the big
ol' elephant in the room.

58:00.408 --> 58:02.510
