58:06.515 --> 58:08.917
Oh, is that the time? I've got a friend to meet!

58:12.988 --> 58:16.425
<i>♪ Silence ♪</i>

58:16.457 --> 58:22.597
<i>♪ Is your friend ♪</i>

58:22.631 --> 58:26.335
