59:20.222 --> 59:22.258
intentionally being
controversial

59:22.290 --> 59:23.258
to, uh...

59:29.964 --> 59:31.367
Court publicity.

59:33.035 --> 59:35.004
...to court publicity.

59:35.037 --> 59:36.437
Is it true?

59:36.470 --> 59:38.306
You mean,
is it autobiographical?

59:38.339 --> 59:40.309
No! I don't care
about the sexy stuff.

59:40.341 --> 59:43.678
Come on!
What year is this? 1955?

59:43.711 --> 59:45.347
But apparently,

59:45.379 --> 59:48.117
