in the book that's designed

59:48.149 --> 59:50.618
to get someone arrested
if they read it on a plane.

59:51.687 --> 59:52.922
That's just a joke,

59:52.955 --> 59:54.156
nobody would take it seriously,

59:54.189 --> 59:55.091
surely.

59:57.392 --> 59:59.395
